{"tid":1468601,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地係捍衛緊人權 自己踩過界咁憑咩擁有","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:52:12.000Z","uid":282134,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78d45853dc709f16e1c49e2fce18feec5bfed43e","tid":1468601,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:20.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n我不割席 不分化 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但人權係適用於任何人 同樣適用於對方</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係屌今日做嘅野 而係想提點返呢一樣野 同埋唔洗再互屌啦 大家唔好俾對面成功分化 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地都係喺一條船駛緊向同一個目的地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好諗返之後嘅計劃啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"298cabfae4e1dcd4e1a93dda17f561cb1e003796","tid":1468601,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:28:31.000Z","msg":"唔認為係教條主義<br />\n我都火遮眼過 我今日都想打柒個共狗"},{"pid":"885a5318d15c38734135cbcec1dc8857eea01467","tid":1468601,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:29:27.000Z","msg":"推吧"},{"pid":"8da7fd1958f4298317adb912103efd2c71148441","tid":1468601,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:52:12.000Z","msg":"間諜不受日內瓦公約保護。"}]}